collections.title: San Lorenzo Tickets & Experiences
collections.descriptionHtml:
Team:

The Club Atletico San Lorenzo de Almagro, also known as San Lorenzo, was founded on April 1, 1908 in the city of Buenos Aires, Argentina. He is considered one of the 5 great teams of his country. San Lorenzo has more than 20 titles in his history: many local championships, 2 national cups. Internationally has 1 Copa Libertadores, 1 Sudamericana and 1 Mercosur.

Buy your San Lorenzo tickets and experience the argentinian football like never before.

Stadium:

The Pedro Bidegain stadium, popularly known as "El Nuevo Gasometro", is located in the City of Buenos Aires and has a capacity of 47,964 spectators.

Get your Pedro Bidegain tickets and enjoy the match with local fans. Definetely, your best football experience!
